data.description: Look at all the charm and curb appeal this home has!! Not an inch of wasted space in this home. There is a good flow to this home and plenty of space for storage. The rooms are a good size and the kitchen is plenty spacious enough for several people to work on their inner chef! The basement has a wonderful laundry area and another good sized room! The roof is metal, the detached garage connects to the covered carport for extra parking, and the lovely covered patio offers shade on sunny days and protection on the rainy days!! This cute cottage is turn key and ready to be moved into. Enjoy the location and being close to all schools and amenities. I-84 access is minutes away and all the shopping is close by.
